CustomField.description: Defines how many Timesheets will be processed when the InvokeEstimatedInterpretationProcess is invoked. A max of 15 will be allowed by the invocable class. When left blank the default batch size of 5 will be used.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Defines how many Timesheets will be processed when the InvokeEstimatedInterpretationProcess is invoked. A max of 15 will be allowed by the invocable class. When left blank the default batch size of 5 will be used.
CustomField.label: Estimated Interpretation Batch Size
